            <lg xml:id="TK426">
<l>evva tuṟaiva tulaka mulakattō</l>
<l>ṭavva tuṟaiva taṟivu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>his is to wisely live and well. To live as the world lives, is wisdom.</l>
            </lg>
